oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Boy Scout Troop 88 eating at a table
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Group photograph of Boy Scout Troop 88 eating at a table. They are spending the night at a cabin in Miller's Cove of the Great Smokey Mountains. Russell Willis Hillis (1914�1992), scout leader, is seated at the head of the table.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:coverage: Great Smoky Mountains National Park (N.C. and Tenn.)

oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Guides & scouts
